Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:04:02.01,OP/ED English,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:236760,242010}{\fad(0,400)}Come walk with us{NOTE:僕ら一緒に歩いていこうよ}
Comment: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:04.05,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:244056,244056}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.64,Episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:244640,248644}{\fad(500,600)\pos(602,480)}Episode 70\NA Rider Called Anvis{NOTE:第７０話\\Nアンブィスというライダー}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.43,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:244849,246434}What?{NOTE:え～っ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.31,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:246434,249312}Avinia got caught again!?{NOTE:アユリアまた捕まっちゃったのかよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.89,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:250438,252899}Even if you did manage to get us here again…{NOTE:私を捕らえたとしても…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.19,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:252899,255193}…we won't cooperate with you.{NOTE:…あなたの思いどおりにはならないでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:20.23,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:256277,260239}Heh, so you think your brother will resist me?{NOTE:フッ。兄はお前を助けないというのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:22.32,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:260239,262325}Brother. What should we do?{NOTE:兄さん。なすべきことを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.91,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:264202,267914}Your father gave in to me eventually.{NOTE:かつてお前たちの父も私に屈した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.04,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:267914,271042}Your brother will surely do the same.{NOTE:兄もまた同じことをするだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.21,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:271042,272210}My father?{NOTE:父も？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.37,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:272210,274378}As the only survivors of Kuang Village…{NOTE:クアン村の生き残り…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:38.09,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:274378,278090}…your precious lives still have a role to fulfill.{NOTE:…その貴重な命存分に役立てるがいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.76,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:280218,282762}When did you realize my true identity?{NOTE:いつから俺の正体を知っていた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.51,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:282762,284514}I've said it already.{NOTE:言ったはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.76,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:284514,286766}I knew you'd be useful some day.{NOTE:いずれお前は役に立つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.93,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:286766,288935}At least, that was my intuition.{NOTE:そう直感したと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:53.73,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:288935,293731}When I saw you for the first time,\NI felt something.{NOTE:そしてひと目お前を見たときから何かを感じていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.44,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:293731,296442}At the beginning, I wasn't sure what it was.{NOTE:ただならぬ何かをな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.31,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:296442,298319}But after some time passed…{NOTE:その後時を経て…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.40,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:298319,301405}…it all became clear to me.{NOTE:…その思いは確信に変わったのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:07.87,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:301405,307870}You are the only one who can make the Rite of Overlapping a success.{NOTE:お前こそが重ね合わせの儀を成功させられるただ一人の者であると。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:12.12,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:308204,312124}And here you thought you were taking every precaution to not get caught…{NOTE:バレないように調子よくうまくやってたつもりだろうが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.25,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:312124,314252}I guess all your efforts went to waste, huh?{NOTE:…バレバレだったってことだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.84,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:320967,322844}I like that look.{NOTE:その目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.97,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:322844,325972}Eyes that deceive people.{NOTE:人を欺かんとする瞳。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.51,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:325972,328516}Eyes that are plotting something.{NOTE:何かをたくらんでいる瞳。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:35.48,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:330017,335481}The light of anger in the back of the eyes\Nthat cannot be hidden no matter how much you try.{NOTE:隠しているつもりでも隠しきれない瞳の奥の怒りの光。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.06,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:337525,340069}It's the same as mine.{NOTE:かつての私と同じだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.11,Default,Gale's father,0,0,0,,{TIME:340653,342113}What are you thinking?{NOTE:何を思い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.28,Default,Gale's father,0,0,0,,{TIME:342113,344282}What are you hiding?{NOTE:何を隠している？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.03,Default,Gale's father,0,0,0,,{TIME:344282,345032}Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:50.20,Default,Gale's father,0,0,0,,{TIME:346659,350204}The light behind your eyes tells me everything.{NOTE:瞳の奥の光は全てを語る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.41,Default,Gale's father,0,0,0,,{TIME:350204,353416}{\t(2495,3212,\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)\fad(0,100)}How cloudy your mind is.{NOTE:お前の曇った心の全てを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:356961,358838}I'm nothing like you.{NOTE:一緒にするな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.25,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:358838,360256}We're the same.{NOTE:同じだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:04.13,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:360256,364135}I wanted the power and used betrayal to get it.{NOTE:私は力を欲し裏切りを決意した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:08.01,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:364135,368014}I never betrayed you.{NOTE:俺はお前を裏切る気なんか毛頭ないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.55,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:368014,371559}I've never even obeyed you to begin with.{NOTE:最初からただの一度も従ってなどいなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.97,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:371559,372977}Well.{NOTE:よかろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:17.60,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:372977,377607}You still have a strong desire for revenge inside you.{NOTE:お前にはお前の復讐という名の思いが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.61,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:377607,381611}And I have my great ambition.{NOTE:私には私の大いなる野望が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:25.74,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:381611,385740}I'm afraid that's the only difference between us.{NOTE:運悪く相いれない思いであるだけのこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:385740,388409}How could you kill our father and mother!?{NOTE:よくも父さんと母さんを！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.16,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:388409,391162}It was your father's fault.{NOTE:お前の父が悪いのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.87,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:391162,393873}He didn't do as I said.{NOTE:私の言うとおりにしなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.45,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:393873,395458}Shut up!{NOTE:黙れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:395458,397627}My father did the right thing.{NOTE:父は正しいことをした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:42.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:397627,402048}And if you hadn't done that back then…{NOTE:そしてあの日お前があんなことをしなければ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:46.09,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:402048,406093}…maybe our village wouldn't have been wiped out from the Black Blight.{NOTE:…黒の凶気で村が全滅することもなかったかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.84,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:406886,407844}Brother…?{NOTE:兄さん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.01,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:409305,412016}I'm sorry I didn't know anything.{NOTE:何も知らなくてごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.39,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:412016,414393}You have nothing to apologize for.{NOTE:お前が謝ることじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:414393,416520}This is all his fault.{NOTE:全てあいつが悪い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.98,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:416520,418981}You still don't understand me.{NOTE:お前に私の思いは分からぬ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:05.98,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:420608,425988}I've always been in everyone else's shadow since I was born.{NOTE:生まれ落ちて以来ずっと日陰の身であり続ける定めだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.24,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:426781,429241}Don't you understand?{NOTE:私の思いが分かるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:14.49,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:429241,434497}You did promise to help me in my\Nquest to obtain the ultimate power, didn't you?{NOTE:日の当たる場所で神々しい力を得ることを約束されたお前に！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.74,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:435665,436749}Why…?{NOTE:なぜ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.74,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:436749,438749}Why do you even want that power?{NOTE:…そうまでして力を手に入れたい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.50,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:440835,442505}Do you really want to know?{NOTE:聞きたいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:32.09,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:444340,452098}As Kuang Village's priests,\Nyour clan was always prosperous.{NOTE:お前たち一族はクアン村の神官としていかなるときもあがめ奉られていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:39.23,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:452098,459230}Just because you happened to be responsible for keeping the secret of the Rite of Overlapping.{NOTE:一子相伝の秘術である、重ね合わせの儀をつかさどる一族というだけで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.35,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:459230,460356}But, on the other hand…{NOTE:引き換え…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:46.36,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:460356,466362}…there was my family who was in a position\Nof looking after your priests for generations.{NOTE:…私の一族は代々お前たち神官を世話する立場にあった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.94,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:466362,469949}But there's no sunlight without a shadow.{NOTE:だが光と影は共にあるもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:59.20,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:471741,479208}As someone who looked over your family,\NI eventually saw the Rite.{NOTE:私はお前たち一族が隠し守り続けていた秘術をこの目で見ていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.71,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:479207,483713}I learned as much as I could back then.{NOTE:そしてそのほとんどを知り得てもいた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.67,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:483713,485673}I asked myself why…?{NOTE:であるのになぜ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:12.05,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:485673,492054}Why was it only your clan that was allowed to perform the ritual? Why couldn't I do it?{NOTE:…お前たち一族のみが秘術を使うことを許され私は許されないのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.05,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:492054,495057}So I began to doubt the system.{NOTE:そんな疑問が生まれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.18,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:495057,497184}It's only natural.{NOTE:そりゃそうですよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.18,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:497184,499184}It just wasn't fair.{NOTE:不公平ってもんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.52,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:499184,502523}So I asked your father.{NOTE:だから私はお前の父に尋ねた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:27.82,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:502523,507820}"Why is it just your family that gets to keep the secret?"{NOTE:なぜあなた方一族のみが秘術を伝え合うのかと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:507820,509905}What did my father do?{NOTE:父は何と？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.74,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:509905,511741}Did he really say we were the chosen ones?{NOTE:選ばれし者とでも言ったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.36,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:512742,515369}What he said was:{NOTE:こう言った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:41.50,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:515369,521500}"When one has wicked thoughts,\Nonly the family can take the responsibility."{NOTE:よこしまな思いを抱いたときに責任を取れるのは血族だけと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:49.00,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:523878,529008}"Then, if you think I have a wicked heart, punish me!"{NOTE:では私がよこしまな思いを抱いたらどうぞ罰してください！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.63,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:529008,531635}"Otherwise, teach me the Rite!"{NOTE:だから私にも秘術を！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.88,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:531635,533888}I begged to teach me.{NOTE:私はそう懇願した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.72,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:535306,536724}However…{NOTE:だが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:01.02,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:536724,541020}{\t(2629,4629,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)\fad(0,300)}He never granted my wish.{NOTE:その願いが聞き入れられる日は来なかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:08.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:542938,548194}So you took our mother hostage\Nand forced our father to give the Rite up?{NOTE:それで母を人質にして、父に秘術を施すことを強要したのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:12.15,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:549278,552156}What other choice did I have?{NOTE:他に方法があったとでも？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.86,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:552156,554867}Your father didn't trust me.{NOTE:お前の父は私を信用しなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.49,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:554867,558496}And that's what caused the tragedy.{NOTE:そのせいであの悲劇が起こった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.33,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:558496,560331}What is he talking about?{NOTE:いったい何が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.20,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:560331,563209}I guess you were young, so you can't remember it…{NOTE:お前は幼かったから覚えていないだろうが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.67,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:564126,566670}He took our mother hostage…{NOTE:あいつは母を人質にし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:566670,568756}…and forced our father to perform the ritual on him.{NOTE:…父に秘術を強要した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.96,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:570049,571967}I want to become strong.{NOTE:強くなりたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:35.34,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:571967,575346}I want to become a Rider superior to everyone else!{NOTE:よりライダーとしての高みへ上り詰めたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.59,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:575346,578599}It was inevitable that would happen.{NOTE:そう思うのは必然だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.72,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:578599,579725}However…{NOTE:しかし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:45.77,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:579725,585773}Your father performed a false ritual\Nand didn't give the power to me.{NOTE:お前の父は偽の儀式を行い私に力を与えはしなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.99,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:596325,599995}What happened to your parents\Nis a punishment for that.{NOTE:お前の父と母に起きたことはその報いだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:03.08,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:599995,603082}He should've known better and performed the real thing.{NOTE:私に偽の秘術を施した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.71,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:604875,607711}You don't understand anything after all.{NOTE:やっぱりお前は何も分かってない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:607711,610131}My father didn't do a fake ritual on you.{NOTE:父は偽の秘術など行わなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:17.13,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:612633,617138}It was just that you didn't deserve the Rite of Overlapping.{NOTE:お前が重ね合わせの儀を受けるに値しない者だっただけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.26,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:617138,619265}The Rite's failure only proved it.{NOTE:儀式がそれを証明したんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.14,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:620182,623144}And yet here I am, still alive.{NOTE:だが私はこうして生きている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:28.10,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:623144,628107}And thanks to that ceremony\NI gained a stronger power than before.{NOTE:かつあの儀式のおかげでそれ以前よりも強い力を得た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.23,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:628107,631235}And now I also have a hostage.{NOTE:そして…人質もいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.69,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:631944,634697}You'll perform the ritual in your father's place.{NOTE:父に代わってお前がやり遂げるのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.49,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:634697,637491}You don't want that day to repeat, do you?{NOTE:あの日を繰り返したくはないだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:41.03,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:637491,641036}And you surely don't want to sacrifice your sister.{NOTE:妹を犠牲にすることになるのだからな。}
